				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 1 0><gold>1 - So you're a thief as well a mage?" to the player
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 2 0><gold>2 - Alright, then. What did you need me for?" to the player
		#Merriam - Meeting Elaboration
		else if arg 1 is 1:
			if arg 2 is 0:
				send formatted "<light blue>Merriam: <white>Look, it wasn't intentional! I forgot to put it back after I got transferered, okay?" to the player
				wait 3 seconds
				send formatted "<light blue>Merriam: <white>I don't think he'd mind it much anyways, just as long as he knew I was putting it to good use." to the player
