				send formatted "<light blue>Merriam: If you do try and argue with him, please leave the rest of us out of it. When Lex tried it, Alastor nearly suspended all of us for a week." to the player
				wait 3.5 seconds
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 3 3><gold>1 - What did Lex try to argue about?" to the player
				#send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 3 4><gold>2 - I fear no man. Alastor needs to be taken down a peg for insulting me like this." to the player
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 4 0><gold>3 - I'll drop it, then. Anything else with that mission you mentioned?" to the player
			else if arg 2 is 3:
				send formatted "<light blue>Merriam: <white>He got really offended when Alastor called him a meathead. You can probably guess what happens next." to the player
				wait 3 seconds
				send formatted "<light blue>Merriam: <white>"
		#Merriam - Convo End Positive
		else if arg 1 is 4:
			send formatted "<light blue>Merriam: <white>I think that's all of it. Good luck with it, %player's tablist name%<reset><white>!" to the player
			startQuest(player,"COS_QUEST_PART1_04","Alastor has a new mission for you at House Ulster.")
		#Alastor
		else if arg 1 is 5:
			if arg 2 is 0:
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>Jagen says he was tipped off by someone that a large number of monsters are coming into the village. Normally I don't let anonymous sources have much of a say in what I do, but I know Jagen wouldn't have brought it to my attention if he didn't believe it himself." to the player
				wait 7 seconds
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>That man's seen and done a hell of a lot more than any single person should. If he's asking for help, then we'd better be taking it seriously." to the player
				wait 5 seconds
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 1><gold>1 - Who is Jagen, exactly?" to the player
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 2><gold>2 - If that's the case, then why send me?" to the player
			else if arg 2 is 1:
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>Jagen was a soldier in Cinder's army while he was still the lone ruler of Silgrund." to the player
				wait 5 seconds
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>That man was a good soldier. Damn good. He didn't even need to raise his lance to send bandits running home to their mothers." to the player
				wait 5 seconds
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>Now this was years ago, mind you. He's gotten old, and he's sure as hell out of his prime. He can still put up a fight, but nobody's going to be calling him to war." to the player
				wait 6 seconds
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 2><gold>1 - Why send me on this mission?" to the player
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 4><gold>2 - I'll be on my way." to the player
			else if arg 2 is 2:
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>Well, I'm still skeptical about his source for this monster siege. I don't want to send my best knights off just to squash a spider, so I figure someone like you would be better suited to the task." to the player
				wait 6 seconds
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 1><gold>1 - Who is Jagen, exactly?" to the player
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 3><gold>2 - Thanks for letting me know my worth to you." to the player
				send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 5 4><gold>3 - I'll be on my way." to the player
			else if arg 2 is 3:
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>You asked, I delivered." to the player
				wait 3 seconds
				send formatted "<light blue>Alastor: <white>Now, if you're done complaining, start heading over to Ram Village and see what Jagen has in store for you." to the player
				wait 3 seconds
				if {str.%player%} + {strbuff.%player%} is more than 14:
					send formatted "<run command:/quests-COS_QUEST_PART1_04 6 0><light green>1 - I don't think you're taking me seriously. [STR >= 15]" to the player
